**Summary:** This documentation covers Amplitude Data's Google Ads event streaming integration that uses the Google Ads Upload Click Conversions API to stream Amplitude events directly to Google Ads, requiring Google Click ID (gclid) and Conversion Date Time properties for conversion tracking and attribution.

